{"Name":"Add Comment to Detection","Description":"Deprecated. Add a comment to the detection in Crowdstrike Falcon.","Script":"from SiemplifyAction import SiemplifyAction\nfrom SiemplifyUtils import output_handler\nfrom ScriptResult import EXECUTION_STATE_COMPLETED, EXECUTION_STATE_FAILED\n\nfrom TIPCommon.extraction import extract_configuration_param, extract_action_param\n\nfrom constants import (\n    API_ROOT_DEFAULT,\n    INTEGRATION_NAME,\n    ADD_COMMENT_TO_DETECTION_SCRIPT_NAME,\n)\nfrom CrowdStrikeManager import CrowdStrikeManager\n\n\n@output_handler\ndef main():\n    siemplify = SiemplifyAction()\n    siemplify.script_name = ADD_COMMENT_TO_DETECTION_SCRIPT_NAME\n\n    siemplify.LOGGER.info(\"----------------- Main - Param Init -----------------\")\n\n    api_root = extract_configuration_param(\n        siemplify,\n        provider_name=INTEGRATION_NAME,\n        param_name=\"API Root\",\n        default_value=API_ROOT_DEFAULT,\n    )\n    client_id = extract_configuration_param(\n        siemplify, provider_name=INTEGRATION_NAME, param_name=\"Client API ID\"\n    )\n    client_secret = extract_configuration_param(\n        siemplify, provider_name=INTEGRATION_NAME, param_name=\"Client API Secret\"\n    )\n    use_ssl = extract_configuration_param(\n        siemplify,\n        provider_name=INTEGRATION_NAME,\n        param_name=\"Verify SSL\",\n        input_type=bool,\n        is_mandatory=True,\n    )\n    customer_id = extract_configuration_param(\n        siemplify,\n        provider_name=INTEGRATION_NAME,\n        param_name=\"Customer ID\",\n        print_value=True,\n    )\n\n    siemplify.LOGGER.info(\"----------------- Main - Started -----------------\")\n\n    detection_id = extract_action_param(\n        siemplify, param_name=\"Detection ID\", is_mandatory=True\n    )\n    comment = extract_action_param(siemplify, param_name=\"Comment\", is_mandatory=True)\n\n    result_value = True\n    status = EXECUTION_STATE_COMPLETED\n\n    try:\n        manager = CrowdStrikeManager(\n            client_id=client_id,\n            client_secret=client_secret,\n            use_ssl=use_ssl,\n            api_root=api_root,\n            customer_id=customer_id,\n        )\n\n        detection_status = manager.get_detection_status(detection_id)\n        manager.add_comment_to_detection(comment, detection_id, detection_status)\n\n        output_message = (\n            f\"Successfully added comment to detection with identifier: {detection_id}.\"\n        )\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        output_message = f\"Error executing action '{ADD_COMMENT_TO_DETECTION_SCRIPT_NAME}'. Reason: {e}\"\n        status = EXECUTION_STATE_FAILED\n        siemplify.LOGGER.error(output_message)\n        siemplify.LOGGER.exception(e)\n        result_value = False\n\n    siemplify.LOGGER.info(\"----------------- Main - Finished -----------------\")\n    siemplify.LOGGER.info(\n        f\"\\n  status: {status}\\n  is_success: {result_value}\\n  output_message: {output_message}\"\n    )\n    siemplify.end(output_message, result_value, status)\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n","IntegrationIdentifier":"CrowdStrikeFalcon","ScriptResultName":"is_success","DynamicResultsMetadata":null,"Creator":"Admin","IsEnabled":true,"IsCustom":true,"AiGenerated":false,"IsSystem":false,"Version":1.0,"TimeoutSeconds":600,"IsAsync":null,"AsyncPollingIntervalInSeconds":300,"TotalIntervalTimeoutForAsyncInSeconds":3600,"Parameters":[{"CustomActionId":0,"IsMandatory":true,"DefaultValue":"","Description":"Specify the id of the detection to which you want to add a comment.","Name":"Detection ID","Value":"","Type":0,"OptionalValues":null,"OptionalValuesJson":null},{"CustomActionId":0,"IsMandatory":true,"DefaultValue":"","Description":"Specify the comment that needs to be added to the detection.","Name":"Comment","Value":"","Type":0,"OptionalValues":null,"OptionalValuesJson":null}],"DefaultResultValue":"","PythonVersion":"None","ActionType":1,"SimulationData":{"Entities":[]},"SimulationDataJson":"{\"Entities\": []}","AICategories":[],"OutcomeCategories":[],"AIDescription":"### General Description\nAdds a comment to a specific detection in CrowdStrike Falcon. This action is used to provide additional context or updates to an existing security detection within the CrowdStrike platform. It first retrieves the current status of the detection to ensure the comment is applied correctly without unintentionally changing the detection's state.\n\n### Parameters Description\n| Parameter | Type | Mandatory | Description |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| Detection ID | String | Yes | The unique identifier of the detection in CrowdStrike Falcon to which the comment will be added. |\n| Comment | String | Yes | The text content of the comment to be appended to the detection. |\n\n### Flow Description\n1. **Parameter Initialization**: The action extracts the necessary configuration (API Root, Credentials) and action parameters (Detection ID, Comment).\n2. **Status Retrieval**: It calls the CrowdStrike API to fetch the current status of the specified Detection ID. This is a prerequisite for the update call.\n3. **Comment Submission**: It sends a PATCH request to the CrowdStrike `detections` endpoint, providing the Detection ID, the comment text, and the previously retrieved status to append the comment.\n4. **Completion**: The action reports success if the comment is successfully added or failure if an error occurs during the API interaction.\n\n### Additional Notes\n- **Deprecation**: This action is marked as deprecated in the integration metadata.\n- **External Mutation**: This action modifies data in the CrowdStrike Falcon platform by adding a comment to a detection record.","AiShortDescription":null,"ParametersDescription":null,"EntityTypes":[]}